      • getGenericType

        @Deprecated
public Type getGenericType()
        已过时。 Since 2.7 should instead use getType(). To be removed from 2.9
        JDK declared generic type of the annotated element; definition of what exactly this means depends on sub-class. Note that such type cannot be reliably resolved without TypeResolutionContext, and as a result use of this method was deprecated in Jackson 2.7: see getType() for replacement.
